$def with (old_life, new_life, country, change)
<html>
<font face="Helvetica">
<p> Right now you have about $round(old_life,2) years left</p>
<p> If you move to $country.capitalize(), you will live about $round(new_life,2) more years.</p>
$if change>0:
	<p> If you move now, your lifespan will increase by $round(change,2) years!</p>
$else: 
	<p> Dude, are you sure? If you move there, your remaining life expectancy will drop by $round(change,2) years!</p>
</font>
</html>
